node.text:
Feral Hogs destroy millions of dollars worth of farm land annually. They ruin habitat for upland game & other native species. @sydnie_wells heads to Bay City, Texas with @ashcraft.aviation to help fight this problem.

@olson.helicopters @jakefoy06 @welldunn_
